      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the<strong> haddock bites</strong> to the pan and cook for 3 min, turning once half way, or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
