      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>miso haddock </strong>with the <strong>sticky rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Serve the <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
